de.charite.compbio.jannovar.pedigree.compatibilitychecker.xd

Class VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerXDominant

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.charite.compbio.jannovar.pedigree.compatibilitychecker.AbstractVariantContextCompatibilityChecker
      • de.charite.compbio.jannovar.pedigree.compatibilitychecker.xd.VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerXDominant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InterfaceVariantContextCompatibilityChecker

    public class VariantContextCompatibilityCheckerXDominant
extends AbstractVariantContextCompatibilityChecker
    Helper class for checking a InheritanceVariantContextList for compatibility with a Pedigree and X dominant mode of inheritance.

    Compatibility Check

    For X-chromosomal dominant inheritance, there must be at least one Genotype that is shared by all affected individuals but no unaffected individuals in the pedigree.
    Version:
    0.15-SNAPSHOT
    Author:
    Manuel Holtgrewe, Max Schubach, Peter N Robinson
